705339f-a.title: Brooklyn: Avenue L - 94th Street (East)
705339f-a.text:
9402-9410 Ave. L., south side, near East 94th Street. Also seen is 1421-1425 East 94th Street, east side, south from Ave. L.
July 6, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.

702932f-a.title: Brooklyn: 94th Street (East) - Avenue L
702932f-a.text:
1451 East 94th Street, east side, between Aves. M and L; a frame house.
July 6, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.

702933f-a.title: Brooklyn: 94th Street (East) - Avenue L
702933f-a.text:
1475 East 94th Street, east side, between Aves. M and L., showing
an old frame house.
July 6, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
